description: North Arrow Minerals Inc. engages in the acquisition and exploration of diamond properties in Canada. The company's principal properties include Naujaat and Mel projects located in Nunavut; the Pikoo project comprises 39,752 hectares of mineral claims located in Saskatchewan; and the Loki Diamond property, including 23 mineral claims that covers approximately 12,898 hectares located in Northwest Territories. It also owns a 100% interest in ORO gold property located in the Hope Bay Volcanic Belt in Nunavut; the Luxx property located in Nunavut; and the CSI property, which comprises 4,540 hectares located in the Nunavut. North Arrow Minerals Inc. is based in Vancouver, Canada.
